snippet.textDisplay: On 20th May, 2024 I was on a Tejas Express to New Delhi. It was AC Chair class, and the screen above was playing different music videos. As soon as my stop at GZB had to arrive, this song started playing. I was still looking at the screen, but at 0:50 , the absolute prettiest transition ever I've heard in music, I noticed all eyes in the train lift up, lit up. Everyone was mesmerized. One of the most GOLDEN moments of my life! ❤️✨️
snippet.textOriginal: On 20th May, 2024 I was on a Tejas Express to New Delhi. It was AC Chair class, and the screen above was playing different music videos.
